user.biography: let the world be your canvas 🍃

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by noor! on August 18, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: i miss the days when instagram was primarily a photo sharing app and not just an imitation of tiktok. id love to post more photos but as a freelancer i feel a need to prioritize creation of content that the algorithm will prioritize (reels). ive used instagram for almost seven years now and i find myself disliking it more and more with every update and change, but i stay on it out of necessity (again, because im a freelancer). whatever. here are some photos from my summer that i like. have a nice day y’all.
